                    <div class="hero-inner">
						<div class="hero-copy">
	                        <h1 class="hero-title mt-0">LK Convert</h1>
	                        <p class="hero-paragraph">By keeping it clean, simple, and all about user experience, LKConvert has become the most loved and trusted LKConvert software on the planet, and the first and only LKConvert software you’ll love.</p>
	                        <div class="hero-cta">
								
							</div>
						</div>
